1.title: Born of the Storm

episode of.title: Dark Days in Monkey City (TV Series 2009– )

1.plot: The Temple Troop has dominated Monkey City for years, but times are changing. Internal friction and power plays for the throne weaken them. And their ancient foes, the Black Claws, dream of overthrowing them and their home - the food-rich Fig Tree Vale.

2.title: To Be King

episode of.title: Dark Days in Monkey City (TV Series 2009– )

2.plot: Aging king Lear must fend off potential rebellion for hiw crown within the Temple Troop. Meanwhile, the Temple Troop's ancient foes, the Black Claws, are streetwise and thirsting for battle. War is brewing in Monkey City.

3.title: Invasion of the Black Claws

episode of.title: Dark Days in Monkey City (TV Series 2009– )

3.plot: The aging Lear's benign leadership has come to a bloody end. The brutal new King Hector is using any excuse to exert his authority. Meanwhile, the Black Claws make their initial plot to take over Fig Tree Vale.

4.title: Battle for Fig Tree Vale

episode of.title: Dark Days in Monkey City (TV Series 2009– )

4.plot: When the Black Claws launch a full-scale attack, Fig Tree Vale becomes a savage battleground, where heroes meet their bloody end. Only one tribe will remain to rule in these Dark Days in Monkey City.

imdb.plot outline: Deep in the jungles of Sri Lanka, the ruins of an ancient civilization are now a savage battlefield. Welcome to Monkey City. Rival tribes of toque macaques are battling for supremacy among the ruined temples. The weak will be banished from Monkey City and into the Badlands, or worse - the human hell that lies across the river. This is an epic story about the fall and rise of the Temple Troop, the mightiest tribe in Monkey City, and the courage of its humblest female. The dramatic fight for survival amongst the macaque tribes has never been bloodier than in these dark days in Monkey City.
